      "gloss_en_full": "An often humorous, freely invented remark or passage in scholarly works or encyclopedia articles (and nowadays also in software source code) that brings joy to both the author while writing and the reader upon discovering it; such easter eggs can span the length of an entire article or even a complete work.",
